Package: RNewsflow
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Analyzing Content Homogeneity and News Diffusion using Computational Text Analysis
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2019-03-23
Author: Kasper Welbers & Wouter van Atteveldt
Maintainer: Kasper Welbers <kasperwelbers@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of tools for measuring the similarity of news content and tracing the flow of (news) messages over
    time and across media. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.2.0), 
    igraph,
    tm,
    Matrix (>= 1.2)
